column2: SELECT TOP # G.objID, mn.ldist_z, G.u, G.g, G.r, G.i, G.z, a.*, emline.z as z_noqso, emline.sigmaStars as emline_vdisp, pca.vdisp_median as pca_vdisp, sp.veldisp as sp_vdisp FROM Galaxy as G join GalSpecLine as a on G.SpecobjID = a.SpecObjID join stellarMassPCAWiscBC0# AS pca ON G.specobjid = pca.specobjid join emissionLinesPort as emline on pca.specobjid = emline.specobjid JOIN specObj as sp ON emline.specobjid = sp.specobjid JOIN mangaDAPall as mn on G.htmID = mn.htmID
